        <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>SNAP_SETTLE adds the prototype-missing jump handling: deltas above the readout&apos;s snapThreshold teleport the tape near the target, then ease the final step, so a sudden 130→250 KIAS change doesn&apos;t spin every wheel through 120 intermediate values. </para>
